<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/23083861">三国时期有谁是刘备，曹操和孙权三人都见过的？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1414532" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">庞统应该可以算一个，还有吗？<br><b>最好列出史书分别对该人与此三人见面的记载。</b></div>


