<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$huang-liang-81-77" href="/people/huang-liang-81-77">黄粱</a>，<strong title="三国圈刷题用户/诗词圈打油玩家/爆照圈自黑能手" class="zu-question-my-bio">三国圈刷题用户/诗词圈打油玩家/爆照圈自…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="22">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liang-yi-zheng" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liang-yi-zheng" class="zg-link" title="梁奕正">梁奕正</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhao-ben-shan-44" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhao-ben-shan-44" class="zg-link" title="夜寐星城">夜寐星城</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-da-er-91" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-da-er-91" class="zg-link" title="王大二">王大二</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1414532" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">谢一页书邀。<br><br>K神大部分都说了，至于有知友说庞统阚泽见过曹吉利，赵云见过渣权之类，显然是受到演义的影响。<br><br>陈登<a data-hash="6cb0c71ef871027c9f4200f008aff31b" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/6cb0c71ef871027c9f4200f008aff31b" class="member_mention" data-editable="true" data-title="@湖海之士陈元龙" data-tip="p$b$6cb0c71ef871027c9f4200f008aff31b">@湖海之士陈元龙</a><br>曾出使许都而后官拜广陵太守，自然见过曹吉利。<br>在徐州多年，文武胆志，湖海之士，自然见过大耳朵。<br>匡琦城下，与渣权两度对阵，亲自引军追奔，短兵相接，想必是见过的，虽然没有辽神那么真切。<br><br><a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/26639497/answer/33495417" class="internal">陈登为什么能两败孙策？ - 黄粱的回答</a>大约是见过的吧，离得那么近，追的那么紧，渣权那时候还那么年轻，肯定跑不快<br><br>至于满宠，与刘备共事许都几个月，也曾和孙权交战过，是否近距离，就不好说了。
<a href="/question/23083861/answer/41772571" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

