<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$si-ma-ji-18" href="/people/si-ma-ji-18">司马祭</a>，<strong title="貌不其扬，一无所长。" class="zu-question-my-bio">貌不其扬，一无所长。</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="60">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wu-zhi-ting-55" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wu-zhi-ting-55" class="zg-link" title="吴致霆">吴致霆</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$cao-yin-5" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/cao-yin-5" class="zg-link" title="曹寅">曹寅</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$jizhongyuegong" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/jizhongyuegong" class="zg-link" title="及众曰公">及众曰公</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1414532" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">刘备。<br>青梅煮酒论英雄，见过曹操。<br>远赴江东娶娇妻，见过孙权。<br>清晨对镜贴花黄，见过刘备。


</div>

